      "text": "* Orders\n    -Jobs?\n    -Takeout vs Dinein\n    -Customers\n* Payment\n* Menu Items\n    - condiments\n    - extras\n* Store orders\n\nFunctional:\n* CRUD on orders, menu itmes, extras\n* Async processing of orders\n* Displayed REST endpoints\n* Separate readers vs writers\n* Message bus + cache\n* Storage of menu items, jobs \nand payment",
      "fontSize": 20,
