      "updated": 1776880999913,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Workflows:\n\n1. Create and store menu items/condiments\n2. Customers create order\n    - choose menu items\n    - choose condiments\n3. Order gets queued for processing\n4. Customers send payment for completed orders\n5. Relevant logs/metrics maintained, Orders/Customers\n    removed from processing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Workflows:\n\n1. Create and store menu items/condiments\n2. Customers create order\n    - choose menu items\n    - choose condiments\n3. Order gets queued for processing\n4. Customers send payment for completed orders\n5. Relevant logs/metrics maintained, Orders/Customers\n    removed from processing",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
